%h4 FAQ

%p Q: “How much time does it take?”

%p A: We’re hoping that this is something you are kinda doing already and that you can link & synch your activities with us. Minimally we’re asking you to commit to some kind of monthly meeting or event and to share at least one story about what you are doing.

%p Q: “What if my city already has an open gov group, leadership structure, or I belong to another open group?"

%p A: That's awesome -- ideal really. We want to support and celebrate your efforts however possible. For the sake of communication though we'd like for one individual to apply to become a Captain. Of course, you're welcome to rotate that throughout the year or share responsibilities.